<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Patch>
  <Operation Class="PatchOperationFindMod">
    <mods>
      <li>Vanilla Expanded Framework</li>
    </mods>
    <nomatch Class="PatchOperationSequence">
      <success>Always</success>
      <operations>
        <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
          <success>Always</success>
          <xpath>/Defs/GeneDef[defName="BotchJob_RottingFleshBasic"]/label</xpath>
          <value>
            <label>썩어가는 살</label>
          </value>
        </li>
        <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
          <success>Always</success>
          <xpath>/Defs/GeneDef[defName="BotchJob_RottingFleshBasic"]/labelShortAdj</xpath>
          <value>
            <labelShortAdj>썩어가는</labelShortAdj>
          </value>
        </li>
        <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
          <success>Always</success>
          <xpath>/Defs/GeneDef[defName="BotchJob_RottingFleshBasic"]/description</xpath>
          <value>
            <description>이 유전자의 보유자는 회색과 초록색이 섞인 썩어가는 피부를 가지게 됩니다.</description>
          </value>
        </li>
      </operations>
    </nomatch>
  </Operation>
  <Operation Class="PatchOperationFindMod">
    <mods>
      <li>[LTS]Systems</li>
    </mods>
    <match Class="PatchOperationSequence">
      <success>Always</success>
      <operations>
        <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
          <success>Always</success>
          <xpath>/Defs/ThingDef[defName="BotchJob_ProfanedGate"]/label</xpath>
          <value>
            <label>불경한 성당 문</label>
          </value>
        </li>
        <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
          <success>Always</success>
          <xpath>/Defs/ThingDef[defName="BotchJob_ProfanedGate"]/description</xpath>
          <value>
            <description>크고 아름다운 이중문입니다. 매우 견고하지만 무겁고 열기 힘듭니다.</description>
          </value>
        </li>
      </operations>
    </match>
  </Operation>
</Patch>